      "effect": "Activate 1 of these effects;\n\u25cf Discard 1 WATER monster to the GY, then target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; destroy it.\n\u25cf Destroy 1 FIRE monster in your hand, then you can draw 1 card.\nIf only your opponent controls a monster: You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 Level 7 or 8 WATER or FIRE monster in your GY; Special Summon it. You can only use each effect of \"Turmoil of Sea and Flames\" once per turn.",
